snippet.title: CLICK, WATCH and DIE LAUGHING - The very funniest ANIMAL videos
snippet.description:
This video is so funny you will die laughing! The hardest try not to laugh challenge! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, bears, hamsters, goats,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
